        {
            "id": "https://bluemap1e.github.io/2023/10/23/C++%20STL%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E2%80%94%E2%80%94string%E7%B1%BB/",
            "url": "https://bluemap1e.github.io/2023/10/23/C++%20STL%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E2%80%94%E2%80%94string%E7%B1%BB/",
            "title": "C++ STL学习——string类",
            "date_published": "2023-10-23T08:04:29.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h2 id=\"前言\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#前言\">#</a> 前言</h2>\n<p>C++ string 类是常用的一种容器，可以很好地取代 C 风格字符串，支持更简便、安全、抽象的操作。</p>\n<p>本文只是一个 STL 自学笔记，实现以下 C++ string 的各种用法，加深记忆，备查备用。</p>\n<p>PS：本文作者是个懒狗，因此他使用了：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><figcaption data-lang=\"C++\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">using</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">namespace</span> std<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr>\n<h2 id=\"头文件\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#头文件\">#</a> 头文件</h2>\n<p>C++ string 类包含于 &lt;string&gt; 头文件中，注意和 &lt; cstring &gt; 进行区分。&lt;cstring &gt; 包含 C 风格字符串的各种函数与工具。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><figcaption data-lang=\"C++\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"token string\">&lt;string></span></span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr>\n<h2 id=\"构造函数\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#构造函数\">#</a> 构造函数</h2>\n<p>C++ 提供了多种 string 类构造函数，能够以不同的方式来初始化一个 string 对象。</p>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"默认构造函数\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#默认构造函数\">#</a> 默认构造函数</h3>\n<h4 id=\"说明\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#说明\">#</a> 说明</h4>\n<p>这是 string 类的默认构造函数，它创建一个空的 string 对象：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><figcaption data-lang=\"C++\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">string</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id=\"示例\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#示例\">#</a> 示例</h4>\n<p>只要像变量一样声明一个 string 对象就行了：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><figcaption data-lang=\"C++\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>string test<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr>\n<h3 id=\"复制构造函数\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#复制构造函数\">#</a> 复制构造函数</h3>\n<h4 id=\"说明-2\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#说明-2\">#</a> 说明</h4>\n<p>通过一个现有的 string 对象来初始化 string 对象，默认的复制构造函数：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><figcaption data-lang=\"C++\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">string</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> string <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span> str<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id=\"示例-2\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#示例-2\">#</a> 示例</h4>\n<p>传入一个现有的 string 对象即可完成初始化：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><figcaption data-lang=\"C++\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>string str1 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Test string.\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>string <span class=\"token function\">test</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>str1<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr>\n<h3 id=\"使用字符串进行初始化\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#使用字符串进行初始化\">#</a> 使用字符串进行初始化</h3>\n<h4 id=\"说明-3\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#说明-3\">#</a> 说明</h4>\n<p>通过传入一个字符串来初始化 string 对象：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><figcaption data-lang=\"C++\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">string</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">char</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> s<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id=\"示例-3\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#示例-3\">#</a> 示例</h4>\n<p>传入一个字符串即可完成初始化：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><figcaption data-lang=\"C++\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>string <span class=\"token function\">test</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Test string.\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr>\n<h3 id=\"使用字符串进行初始化-并指定长度\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#使用字符串进行初始化-并指定长度\">#</a> 使用字符串进行初始化 并指定长度</h3>\n<h4 id=\"说明-4\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#说明-4\">#</a> 说明</h4>\n<p>传入一个字符串与指定的长度：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><figcaption data-lang=\"C++\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">string</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">char</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> s<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id=\"示例-4\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#示例-4\">#</a> 示例</h4>\n<p>可用于截取一个字符串的前 N 个字符，用于初始化：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><figcaption data-lang=\"C++\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>string <span class=\"token function\">test</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"0123456789\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id=\"特殊情况\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#特殊情况\">#</a> 特殊情况</h4>\n<p>这里需要注意，如果指定的长度超出了提供字符串的长度，这种行为<strong>未被定义</strong>，同时编译器也<strong>不会报错</strong>，它会造成 string 对象超出部分的值<strong>未被初始化</strong>：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><figcaption data-lang=\"C++\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>string <span class=\"token function\">test</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"0123456789\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">15</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\t\t<span class=\"token comment\">// 最后的 5 个元素未被初始化</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr>\n<h3 id=\"模板构造函数\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#模板构造函数\">#</a> 模板构造函数</h3>\n<h4 id=\"说明-5\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#说明-5\">#</a> 说明</h4>\n<p>通过模板，将 string 对象初始化为一个指定区间内的字符串，<strong>包括 begin，不包括 end</strong>：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><figcaption data-lang=\"C++\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">template</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">iter</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>string（iter begin<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> iter end<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\t\t<span class=\"token comment\">// 伪代码</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>可以用于截取一个 C 风格字符串等的某个区间，用于初始化新的 string 类：</p>\n<h4 id=\"示例1-截取c风格字符串\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#示例1-截取c风格字符串\">#</a> 示例 1 截取 C 风格字符串</h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><figcaption data-lang=\"C++\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">char</span> str1<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"0123456789\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>string <span class=\"token function\">test</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>str1 <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> str1 <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\t<span class=\"token comment\">//test = \"56789\";</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id=\"示例2-截取c-string\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#示例2-截取c-string\">#</a> 示例 2 截取 C++ string</h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><figcaption data-lang=\"C++\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>string str1 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"0123456789\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>string <span class=\"token function\">test</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span>str1<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span>str1<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\t<span class=\"token comment\">//test = \"56789\";</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr>\n<h3 id=\"顺序截取初始化\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#顺序截取初始化\">#</a> 顺序截取初始化</h3>\n<h4 id=\"说明-6\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#说明-6\">#</a> 说明</h4>\n<p>截取目标字符串从某个位置开始的子串，同时也可以设定截取的长度，这个长度参数是<strong>可选的</strong>，不输入长度参数则代表截取到底：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><figcaption data-lang=\"C++\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">string</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> string <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span> str<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> string size_type pos <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> size_type n <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> npos<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id=\"示例1-截取从某个位置开始-到字符串末尾的整个子串\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#示例1-截取从某个位置开始-到字符串末尾的整个子串\">#</a> 示例 1 截取从某个位置开始 到字符串末尾的整个子串</h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><figcaption data-lang=\"C++\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>string str1 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"0123456789\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>string <span class=\"token function\">test</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>str1<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\t\t\t\t<span class=\"token comment\">//test = \"3456789\";</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id=\"示例2-截取从某个位置开始-固定长度的子串\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#示例2-截取从某个位置开始-固定长度的子串\">#</a> 示例 2 截取从某个位置开始 固定长度的子串</h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><figcaption data-lang=\"C++\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>string str1 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"0123456789\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>string <span class=\"token function\">test</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>str1<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\t\t\t<span class=\"token comment\">//test = \"34567\";</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr>\n<h3 id=\"移动构造函数\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#移动构造函数\">#</a> 移动构造函数</h3>\n<h4 id=\"说明-7\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#说明-7\">#</a> 说明</h4>\n<p>使用另一个 string 对象来初始化当前的 string 对象，将用于初始化的对象的值 “移动” 到当前对象上：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><figcaption data-lang=\"C++\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">string</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>string <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span> str<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">noexcept</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id=\"示例-5\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#示例-5\">#</a> 示例</h4>\n<p>这个例子将 str1 的值转移到 test 当中，操作完成后 str1 是一个空字符串：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><figcaption data-lang=\"C++\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>string str1 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Hello, World!\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>string test <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">move</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>str1<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\t\t<span class=\"token comment\">// 此时 test = \"Hello, world!\" 而 str1 = \"\"</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr>\n<h3 id=\"使用字符列表初始化\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#使用字符列表初始化\">#</a> 使用字符列表初始化</h3>\n<h4 id=\"说明-8\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#说明-8\">#</a> 说明</h4>\n<p>C++11 引入了这样的一个新特性，可以使用字符列表来初始化 string 对象：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><figcaption data-lang=\"C++\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">string</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>initializer_list<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token keyword\">char</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> il<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id=\"示例-6\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#示例-6\">#</a> 示例</h4>\n<p>使用一个显式定义的字符列表来初始化一个 string 对象：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><figcaption data-lang=\"C++\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>string test <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span><span class=\"token char\">'H'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token char\">'e'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token char\">'l'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token char\">'l'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token char\">'o'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\t<span class=\"token comment\">//test = \"Hello\"</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr>\n<p>未完待续……</p>\n",
            "tags": [
                "C++"
            ]
        }
    ]
}